<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>انظر قافية <span class="c2">«الدعاثير»</span>.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>كأن عيني والفِراقُ محذور<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
